overview:
Comprehensive Analysis of Today’s Issues By Tomorrow’s Leaders

GenWhy Press (genwhypress.com) is an aggregate commentary blog that promotes the best civil, non-slanderous, and fact based commentary from all perspectives and sectors of Generation Y in one location.

GenWhy Press is based in Dallas TX. The site is managed by college students and young professionals and only 18-35 year olds can contribute content to the site.

GenWhy Press has established partnerships and syndication networks with many major College University newspapers and in addition to the college newspapers GenWhy Press has partnerships with other young professional bloggers who have a strong following. GenWhy Press shares Generation Y’s perspective on current events and issues.
